Harriet Owen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harriet_Owen 0 Harriet Owen is an English actress from North Brewham, near Bruton, Somerset. She was educated at Prior Park College in Bath, Somerset. She began acting when she was five, appearing in stage and television roles. As a teenager, she voiced the part of Wendy's daughter Jane in the 2002 Disney animated film Return to Never Land.
